comment:
* The Network Suggestion object is used to provide a Wi-Fi network for consideration when * auto-connecting to networks. Apps cannot directly create this object, they must use * {@link WifiNetworkSuggestion.Builder#build()} to obtain an instance of this object. *

* Apps can provide a list of such networks to the platform using * {@link WifiManager#addNetworkSuggestions(List)}.

variables.name: wifiConfiguration
variables.comment:
* Network configuration for the provided network.
     * @hide

variables.name: passpointConfiguration
variables.comment:
* Passpoint configuration for the provided network.
     * @hide

variables.name: isAppInteractionRequired
variables.comment:
* Whether app needs to log in to captive portal to obtain Internet access.
     * @hide

variables.name: isUserInteractionRequired
variables.comment:
* Whether user needs to log in to captive portal to obtain Internet access.
     * @hide

variables.name: isUserAllowedToManuallyConnect
variables.comment:
* Whether app share credential with the user, allow user use provided credential to
     * connect network manually.
     * @hide

variables.name: isInitialAutoJoinEnabled
variables.comment:
* Whether the suggestion will be initialized as auto-joined or not.
     * @hide

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(Parcel dest, int flags)
public WifiConfiguration getWifiConfiguration()
methods.comment:
* Get the {@link WifiConfiguration} associated with this Suggestion.
     * @hide

methods.name: public MacAddress getBssid()
methods.comment:
* Get the BSSID, or null if unset.
     * @see Builder#setBssid(MacAddress)

methods.name: public PasspointConfiguration getPasspointConfig()
methods.comment:
* Get the {@link PasspointConfiguration} associated with this Suggestion, or null if this
     * Suggestion is not for a Passpoint network.

methods.name: public String getSsid()
methods.comment:
* Return the SSID of the network, or null if this is a Passpoint network.
     * @see Builder#setSsid(String)

methods.name: public WifiEnterpriseConfig getEnterpriseConfig()
methods.comment:
* Get the WifiEnterpriseConfig, or null if unset.
     * @see Builder#setWapiEnterpriseConfig(WifiEnterpriseConfig)
     * @see Builder#setWpa2EnterpriseConfig(WifiEnterpriseConfig)
     * @see Builder#setWpa3EnterpriseConfig(WifiEnterpriseConfig)

methods.name: public String getPassphrase()
methods.comment:
* Get the passphrase, or null if unset.
     * @see Builder#setWapiPassphrase(String)
     * @see Builder#setWpa2Passphrase(String)
     * @see Builder#setWpa3Passphrase(String)

methodNames: public void writeToParcel(Parcel dest, int flags)
